Ren will be used to mint Elders which will become the genesis collection! With well over 6 months of mints planned there is always something new to look forward to! My current strategy is to continue and stack up $REN and prepare for elders as they will be the most valuable

(only about 200 elves left), You can also use $REN to find new weapons and items. There are many more use cases for $REN in the future but I am overwhelmingly bullish on this game, not only because of how much passive income I'm making but also what the dev team has planned!

Either by passive staking or active gameplay by sending your elf out on different game modes. If you are passive staking or actively playing you will earn their currency called $REN, this is the token that is used in all aspects of the game, you can mint more elves with $REN

Why im so bullish and how I am making $200-250 a day playing @EthernalElves!
